            "textpurpose":"Didactics",
            "textentryhtml":"Rectangular with convex sides, 2.75 cm. h (max) x 2.1 cm. w (max). Small gold Mao head in ruby circlewith starburst pattern background against white enamel background with concentric lines representing radio signals coming off a radio tower on top of a globe that has longitude & latitude lines, with 8 flags flying unfurled in the background (behind globe & tower).  Gold rim tapers away at corners.\r\nBack: pin/clasp 1/3 from top; 2 inscriptions, each = 2 lines long: 1immediately under pin, bigger: “努力办好广播为全中国 / 人民和全世界人民服务” ; 2 “中央人民广播电台贈 / 1967.9.15”.\r\n",
